data.title: test_member1
data.description: The first test member. Writes "Hello world from test-member1!" to stdout. Additionally has a function that can be used as a WASM tool.

data.title: test_member2
data.description: The second test member. Writes "Hello world from test-member2!" to stdout, then prints a list of dir entries from the pre-opened directory.

data.title: test_lib
data.description: A test library that holds a single `run_tool` function (created from an attribute macro). Returns "Hello world from test-lib!".
